SUMMARY:Solidarity Dinner: South Seattle
DTSTAMP:20260306T013341Z
DTSTART:20260307T133000Z
DESCRIPTION:Dinner for the people! \\nHelp us cook\\\, serve\\\, eat togeth
	er\\\, and connect with our neighbors. \\nWe feed our community\\\, no que
	stions asked\\\, because we believe in our world where no one goes hungry.
	 \\nSaturdays in South Seattle:\\n-Cooking shift: 1:30-4pm in Tukwila\\n-S
	erving shift: 4:30-7pm at Cafe Red (across the street from the light rail 
	station) \\nTo volunteer for a cooking or serving shift\\\, follow the ins
	tructions here: https://bit.ly/solidaritykitchen \\nWe are also looking fo
	r financial supporters. It costs just $2 to feed a hungry neighbor. Suppor
	t here: https://bit.ly/solidaritydonation\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/
	solidarity-dinner-south-seattle/2026-03-07/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/solidarity-dinner-south-seattle/2026-03-07
	/
LOCATION:Cafe Red\\\, 7148 Martin Luther King Jr Way S\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\
	\, 98118\\\, United States
