SUMMARY:37th LD EWG Steering Committee Endorsement Q&A
DTSTAMP:20260306T013341Z
DTSTART:20260307T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Two candidates have applied for Seattle DSA’s endorsement for t
	he 37th Legislative District Washington State House races – Jaelynn Scott 
	running for the open seat\\\, and Alexander Keo running for the other seat
	 against Sharon Tomiko Santos. Jaelynn’s Q&A is from 5-6PM\\\, and Alexand
	er’s Q&A is from 6-7PM. In this first Q&A session\\\, only Steering Commit
	tee and Local Council members will be allowed to ask questions\\\, but the
	 session will be open to any Seattle DSA member to listen in. A Memberwide
	 Forum​ will be held separately\\\, where any Seattle DSA member can ask q
	uestions. Learn about the requests with the below links: \\nJaelynn Scott 
	Questionnaire \\nAlexander Keo Questionnaire\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/eve
	nt/37th-ld-ewg-steering-committee-endorsement-qa/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
