	n if you haven’t had time to read.  Our biweekly discussions seek to infor
	m strategies for winning a democratic socialist society that thrives ecolo
	gically. All are welcome! \\nWe sit outdoors in a breezeway–dress warm. An
	y questions or difficulty getting the book\\\, please email greennewdeal@s
